.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, townhouse, victorian
City: san-francisco, hamburg, nizza, miami
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, peas, raspberry
1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating raspberry and the victorian house##2
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person eating raspberry is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person eating carrot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| House   | victorian        | cape-cod   | farmhouse | townhouse |
| City         | nizza | san-francisco | hamburg    | miami |
| Food     | peas       | cabbage     | raspberry       | carrot    |

