.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, scooter, motorbike
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, billiard, backgammon
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, chinchilla, rat
1. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the car##2
2. the owner of the rat is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Transport   | helicopter | motorbike      | car       | scooter   |
| Game      | domino   | canasta  | backgammon | billiard     |
| Pet      | guinea-pig     | rat | chinchilla        | fish |

