.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, mystery, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, classical, pop, country
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the fan country is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the fan techno is between the fan country and the owner of the hedgehog##2
6. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | mystery | scientific  | fantasy | action      |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | country  | techno | classical |
| Pet   | goldfish | rat | dog | hedgehog     |

