.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, ambient, rock, reggae
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, november, august
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, purple, ivory, mauve
1. the person who likes mauve is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who likes ivory is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the fan rock is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
6. the fan ambient is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in november##2
7. the fan reggae is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | rock  | ambient    | reggae | classical  |
| Birthday   | november | august       | april        | june    |
| Color         | purple | apricot | mauve  | ivory |

