.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, december, january
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip, bellflower, zinnia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, rock, pop
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the fan blues##1
2. the person who growstulip is between the fan pop and the person who's birthday is in march##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan rock##1
4. the fan rock is on the right of the fan blues##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday         | january  | march | december | september |
| Flower   | lily  | zinnia | tulip   | bellflower         |
| Music-Genre           | blues | rock  | d&b   | pop      |

