.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, july, december
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, trike, boat, tram
City: san-francisco, prague, venice, berlin
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person driving the boat is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the trike is between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Birthday          | december  | september    | july | august       |
| Transport         | tram | trike | airplane  | boat |
| City   | venice   | berlin      | prague  | san-francisco     |

