.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, juice, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, boat, roller, skateboard
House: townhouse, tower, futuristic, colonial
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking fanta and the person driving the boat##2
4. the tower house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
6. the tower house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the colonial house is the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the townhouse house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | juice      | tea | mirinda | fanta |
| Transport         | skateboard   | boat  | train | roller |
| House   | colonial | townhouse   | tower | futuristic |

