.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different games are played: go, canasta, chess, scrabble
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, lawyer, social-worker, accountant
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, canadian, australian
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the canadian is the person playing canasta##1
3. the brazilian is between the lawyer and the social-worker##2
4. the social-worker is between the brazilian and the person playing scrabble##2
5. the social-worker is the australian##1
6. the police-officer is the mexican##1
7. the accountant is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Game    | scrabble  | chess | go | canasta     |
| Job   | police-officer | social-worker   | accountant  | lawyer    |
| Nationality     | mexican        | australian       | brazilian      | canadian |

