3. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the trike and the person who growsbellflower##2
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the firefighter##1
6. the writer is on the far right##1
7. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
