City: san-francisco, london, edinburgh, boston
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian, dutch, american
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the american is between the person who likes ebony and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who likes amber is the dutch##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
6. the person who likes white is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | amber | white  | ebony       | blood-red   |
| City      | san-francisco     | edinburgh | london | boston |
| Nationality        | dutch        | american | malaysian     | nigerian |

