.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bongani, game, prince
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, handball, cricket
House: craftsman, modern, futuristic, farmhouse
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the farmhouse house##1
2. the futuristic house is the game-smoker##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the modern house is between the person who's sport is handball and the game-smoker##2
6. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
7. the modern house is the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar           | bongani | prince | game    | blend   |
| Sport   | handball      | parkour   | cricket | rugby |
| House     | craftsman     | modern       | futuristic        | farmhouse    |

