4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, montecristo, bolivar, fonseca
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, dog, rat
1. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the rat is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the scooter is the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the lizard is between the old-henry-smoker and the person driving the scooter##2
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | skateboard           | scooter         | bike      |
| Cigar     | old-henry | bolivar | fonseca | montecristo |
| Pet   | dog     | lizard         | goat       | rat        |

