.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, western, musical, drama
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, monopoly, chess
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, fish, turtle, rabbit
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
2. the person playing monopoly is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | western | drama           | musical |
| Game       | bridge | monopoly    | whist          | chess   |
| Pet      | turtle  | fish   | rabbit | hedgehog  |

