City: miami, colone, nizza, liverpool
1. the fan disco is the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the fan country is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is between the fan disco and the fan salsa##2
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person traveling to miami##2
7. the fan country is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar      | old-henry | oliveros | pall-mall     | baccarat   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | country        | disco  | trance  |
| City           | miami      | liverpool         | colone | nizza |

