.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, lime, avocado, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, dancing, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, western, thriller, zombie
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is the person eating apricot##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person watching thriller movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food         | lemon        | apricot  | avocado | lime   |
| Hobby       | photography | rock-climbing | dancing    | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero        | thriller     | zombie       | western      |

