.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, family, time-travel
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, badminton, rowing, snowboarding
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre        | time-travel | martial-arts | animation | family |
| Beverage         | iced-tea       | almond-milk     | coffee   | mirinda   |
| Sport   | biathlon | badminton | rowing | snowboarding |

 